{
  "texts": [
    "However, virtual assistants learn from consumers' interactions and preferences to enhance personalization.",
    "They can read natural language requests for more advanced and customized help.",
    "Siri, Alexa, and Google Assistant can schedule reminders, make reservations, and answer complex queries based on user preferences.",
    "I-powered service improvements go beyond chatbots and virtual assistants (Bodemer, 2023).",
    "In healthcare, AI-based systems can evaluate patient data and offer customized treatments."
  ]
}